MIPS: BMIPS: Replace <linux/clk-provider.h> by <linux/of_clk.h>

The Broadcom BMIPS platform code is not a clock provider, and just needs
to call of_clk_init().

Hence it can include <linux/of_clk.h> instead of <linux/clk-provider.h>.

